<i>noun</i>: 아코디언 [], 손풍금 [손풍금] <br>
<ul><li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>아코디언 []</dt><br>
<dd>accordion</dd><br>
<dd>손으로 주름상자를 접었다 폈다 하면서 건반을 눌러 연주하는 악기.</dd><br>
<dd>A musical instrument, whose bellows are folded and unfolded and whose keys are stroked to make sounds.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>손풍금 [손풍금]</dt><br>
<dd>accordion</dd><br>
<dd>늘이고 줄일 수 있는 통과 건반을 눌러 소리를 내는 악기.</dd><br>
<dd>An instrument that is played by expanding and compressing its bellows, or squeezebox, while pressing its keyboard.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>